Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The magical properties of this\Nspell will only have lasting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,effects if you focus on--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How in Equestria does\Nthat pony expect to pass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,her History of the\NWonderbolts exam tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if she's wasting time flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna fly\Nright up to her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell her what I think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,about her lackadaisical\Napproach to studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't she be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Huh?\NHow did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the worst\Nsneak attack ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you giving me the\Nstink eye from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And heard you flying towards me\Nand muttering from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you heard me\Nmuttering then you must know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what I was muttering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, the\NWonderbolts History test.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Big Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really Big\NDeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a test!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A test that will\Ndetermine if you can join
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the newly formed\NWonderbolts Reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And being part of the\NWonderbolts Reserves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,means you'll have\Nthe opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to live your dream\Nas a Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most important\Ntest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, not everypony\Ngets all freaked out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,about tests like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not get all\Nfreaked out about tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your freak-outs are so epic you\Nsing whole "freak-out" arias
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,about freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I may tend to take my\Ntests a little seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean you\Nshouldn't be studying for yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! And I know just the\Npony who can help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to\Nso much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most complete--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And ginormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}book on the History{\i0}\N{\i1}of the Wonderbolts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, but how am I supposed\Nto get what's in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Into here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With my handy dandy Study\NChecklist, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,First up: Reading\Nand Highlighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading and highlighting\Nis the foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of any good study method.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It allows the student to\Nhone in and boil down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what's really important,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,separating the\Ngood from the bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the wheat from the chaff,{\i0}\N{\i1}getting to the crux of things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what\Nyou've got so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By highlighting everything,\Nyou don't really
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,separate the wheat\Nfrom the chaff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the good from the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I am not that tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly reading and highlighting\Nis not your style of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So let's move on to{\i0}\N{\i1}the tried and true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,History Lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it snack time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Recess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we just watch the History\Nof the Wonderbolts movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now just get comfortable\Nand experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the magic of learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to the great\NCelestia/Luna Rift,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no need for the\NEarth, Unicorn, Pegasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or E.U.P.--Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But after Luna's banishment,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Protective Pony{\i0}\N{\i1}Platoons{\i0} were formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the anniversary of the{\i0}\N{\i1}first Celestial Year of Peace,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a celebration was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Headed by General Firefly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An elite team of aerial{\i0}\N{\i1}performers were chosen{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to help commemorate this{\i0}\N{\i1}auspicious occasion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The first performance\Nwas so full of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so highly charged, that magical\Nlightning showered down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everypony was so filled{\i0}\N{\i1}with amazement and wonder{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that General Firefly dubbed\Nthem the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you repeat\Nany of my lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,History lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Rainbow...Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to my favorite\Nstyle of learning: Flashcards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Does that mean\NI'll learn in a flash?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One can only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Purple Dart, the leader\Nof the Wonderbolts in the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,4th Celestial Era was\Nknown for his...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow, did you\Nsee what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No! I was riveted by\Nyour captivating cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After becoming the\Nofficial flying squadron
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for Princess Celestia, she\Nhonored them with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The original Wonderbolts\Nlightning bolt insignia was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With a spit wad? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A spit wad to the eye would\Nhave been no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can horse\Naround like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,then you clearly must\Nbe ready for the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess you're\Nalso ready for a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,pop quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The initials E.U.P.\Nstand for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ernie's Undercooked Pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The original aerial\Nteam performed for...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia's Cereal\NCelebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts were given their\Nname by this famous Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say Colonel Waffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? General\NBlazing Donut Glaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did I ace it or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get one\Nanswer correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard\Nanswers so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so breakfast related.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had taken the\Nofficial test today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My dreams of being\Nin the Wonderbolts Reserves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,would've been totally crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any\Nof this history!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fail, I'm gonna\Nfail, I'm gonna fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe your famous\N"study methods"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't all they're\Ncracked up to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I've used them\Nto study for many a test
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the name of the\Npremiere Wonderbolts choreographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Easy Glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many Pegasi\Nflew in the original squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Princess Celestia's\Nfavorite flight pattern?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Icaranian Sun Salutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I could\Npass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rub it in, why\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't see why I have\Nto take this lousy test anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've proven I'm one of\Nthe best fliers around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing their origin and being\Nable to properly represent them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of Equestria\Nis just as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some history buff like you{\i0}\N{\i1}must've made that up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring us fliers down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing history actually\Nis beneficial, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneficial for eggheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this egghead knows\Nhistory and can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should\Nbecome a Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause you've got wings\Ndoesn't mean you can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're barely able to\Njust get off the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, is that any way\Nto talk to a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have more\Nimportant things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Like prepare Rainbow\Nfor her big test?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried everything,\NFluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but none of my study\Nmethods work for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no offense to your\Nteaching methods, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I may have\Na way to help Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Who's that?\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia and Luna, back\Nwhen they were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gummy's an Earth Pony; Winona's\Na Unicorn and Tank is a Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the E.U.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,helping to protect\Nthe Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you\Ngetting all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was aw--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I give it three "Woo hoos"\NWoo hoo, Woo hoo, Woo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And an extra "Woo"\Nfor good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I give it a\N"Whoa, whoa, what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally confused and\NI just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, your woes,\Nthere Woeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someponies learn through\Ntheatrical presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But other ponies learn\Nthrough musical intervention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Back in ancient times there{\i0}\N{\i1}were the Wonderbolts of old. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ A General named Firefly.{\i0}\N{\i1}Amazing and so bold. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ She brought them all together.\N{\i1}Spreading unity in flight. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Performing at their very best.\N{\i1}With wonder and with might. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Next Admiral Fair Weather{\i0}\N{\i1}and the Colonel Purple Dart. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Gave Wonderbolts a bit of{\i0}\N{\i1}steel along with lots of heart ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ An Admiral named Fairy Flight,\N{\i1}a General called Flash. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Helped the bolts fly super{\i0}\N{\i1}high with style and panache. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Commander Easy Glider was{\i0}\N{\i1}the real cream of the crop. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ For with her wicked moves the\NWonderbolts soared to the top. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Wonderbolts! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Yeah, Wonderbolts! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Wonderbolts! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Yeah, Wonderbolts! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ That is my rappin'{\i0}\N{\i1}History of the Wonderbolts. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Wiki wiki wiki, General{\i0}\N{\i1}this and Colonel that. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ They're the Wonderbolts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ something that{\i0}\N{\i1}rhymes with that ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got to\Nlearn this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am just the\Npony to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity. You look ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ignore that comment\Nout of my desire to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready, Rainbow Dash,\Nfor I am going to take you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on an historical\Nadventure in fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now modeling the rather\Nunattractive, and frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,itchy original Wonderbolts'\Nflying costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, thanks to the\Nvision of Flair de Mare,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Wonderbolts ensemble\Nbecame more streamlined
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in a wonderfully\Nbreathable fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there were\Nfashion hits and misses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just look at those{\i0}\N{\i1}dreadful bell bottoms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What were ponies thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet General Flash\Nrocked these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Pinkie! You're real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not the\Nreal General Flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the 10th leader of\Nthe Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I, Pinkie, am really real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Admiral Fairy Flight,\Nfrom the 7th squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you recognize\NCommander Easy Glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sportin' some\Nsort of get-up worn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by Colonel Purple Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much for my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't you fret, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This fashion show nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't help me\Nlearn nothin' either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what special study\Ntrick do you have, AJ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I could tell you every\Nlittle thing there is to know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,about the history of Apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I picked all that up\Nover years in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as a labor of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then you are up a creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we should just go\Nback to old-fashioned studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at these costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely something resonates\Nwith your inner Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And Granny Smith discovered\Nthe first Granny Smith
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in Phillydelphia when\Nshe was just a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Commander Easy Glider was{\i0}\N{\i1}the real cream of the crop. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, stop rapping! That\Nisn't going to help Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Well, I suggest you put down{\i0}\N{\i1}your silly cards of flash. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ For I know that{\i0}\N{\i1}they cannot help ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ our good friend{\i0}\N{\i1}Rainbow Dash. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No rapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And no apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am never going\Nto pass this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow, I'm sorry\Nabout all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean to\Noverwhelm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. You were\Njust trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too bad I'm too\Ndumb to learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You just learn differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If by "differently"\Nyou mean "not at all"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're totally right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's totally wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anypony that's read\Nmore Daring Do books than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not gonna get\Nme into the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And your knowledge of\Njokes and pranks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is only rivaled by Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great, my years of being{\i0}\N{\i1}a class clown{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}prevented me from actually{\i0}\N{\i1}learning how to learn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smart, creative,\Ninventive, and...Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I know you're upset,\Nbut you don't need to--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost slammed into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were jabbering on so\Nmuch, you didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You were listening and\Ntalking to me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! You're such a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,An experienced flyer like\Nme knows how to multi-task.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,While you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was paying\Nattention to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but was also scanning the sky\Nand the ground for any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying's not just flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to stay{\i0}\N{\i1}safe in the sky,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to hear and{\i0}\N{\i1}see everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}down to the littlest detail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, I saw Apple Bloom,\N{\i1}Sweetie Belle and Scootaloo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}come out of Sugar Cube Corner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And from the looks of it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they had carrot cupcakes{\i0}\N{\i1}with sprinkles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm thinking Big Mac{\i0}\N{\i1}sold a huge order of apples{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to Filthy Rich because I heard{\i0}\N{\i1}him give a very hearty, "Eeyup."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I always make note of\Neverything when I fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to hang out\Nwith a loser like me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for meeting\Nme, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, but how?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've tried every\Nkind of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My way, your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't tried\NRainbow Dash's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, listen up, ponies;\Nhere's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go for a fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Got nothin' better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes but, like you said,\NI'm such a newbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I need all the\Npractice I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I'm sure you'll\Nbecome a great flier in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're\Ngood at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just getting my\Ndreams crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh,read any good books lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd tell you what\Nthey're about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but my brain is\Nas dry as a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of rocks, did\Nyou know Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,grew up on a rock farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go work there,\Nsince I have no other plans
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on now, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't give up on your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems my dream has\Ngiven up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll learn\Nto shine shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig ditches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you'll be\Na Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, give it\Nup! I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So! What do you remember\Nabout that flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Except, after Luna was\Nbanished to the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia needed\Nprotective forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so Earth, Unicorn, and Pegasi\Nformed the E.U.P. Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Protective\NPony Platoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the celebration of the\Nfirst Celestial Year of Peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,an elite flying\Nsquadron performed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,headed by General Firefly\Nwho later named the group
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Easy Glider\Nestablished flight choreography
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that is still used by\Nthe Wonderbolts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But how in Equestria\Ndid that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got that, but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on our first flight, I\Ndiscovered that you catalogue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that happens all\Naround you when you're flying
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,without even thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I made use of your special\Nskills by enlisting everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to help you learn the\NHistory of the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Princess Celestia, banish\Nyou, Princess Luna to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,E!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,U!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,P!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate our first\NCelestial Year of Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's party.\NI'm General Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, my costume is\Nitchy and unattractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm gonna assemble\Nan awesome flying team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call them the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Streamlined style\Nby Flaire de Mare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Admiral Fair Weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Purple Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Admiral Fairy Flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,General Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Easy Glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The History of the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, oh my\Ngosh, oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But it all came from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You learn without\Nknowing you're learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your main focus is flying,{\i0}\N{\i1}but then your brain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is also absorbing lots of{\i0}\N{\i1}other information.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually\Nreally brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I always knew\NI was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rainbow Dash finally learned{\i0}\N{\i1}the History of the Wonderbolts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she's not the only{\i0}\N{\i1}pony that needed a lesson.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I needed to learn something{\i0}\N{\i1}just as important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One way of learning isn't{\i0}\N{\i1}better than another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, everypony is{\i0}\N{\i1}unique and individual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! Whoo!
